latestPosts.caption:
a local fashion girlie’s guide to Wellington 🥝📍in partnership with @remixmagazine and @wellingtonnz AD 

Being born and raised in Pōneke, both the city and I have gone through many changes over the years (you should have seen the pink hair and clubbing days! 👀), but what has never changed is the eclectic, friendly and creative vibe that the Capital has to offer. 

Check out the latest @remixmagazine for all of my favourite spots to eat, shop and take in the amazing culture that makes this this city so special 💕

🏷️ #wellingtonnz #newzealand #nz #shopping

latestPosts.caption:
Fashion mogul @elbeefrivilousfashion is a visionary when it comes to curating your own style 👠👗 Whether it’s a Ganni vest, a pinstripe suit or a crochet headscarf, this local-fashion and inclusivity champion can craft the perfect fit for any piece ✨

Elbee shares her ethos behind her approach to fashion - embracing new silhouettes and textures, focusing on fit and not a sizing tag and letting clothing speak for itself -  she has made it clear, fashion should be fearless 💃🏼
